-- Volkswagen Group First-Half Sales Increase 46% in China, Led by Audi Brand
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-12T08:13:10Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-12/volkswagen-group-first-half-sales-increase-46-in-china-led-by-audi-brand.html

          
          
             Volkswagen AG’s first-half sales in
China gained 46 percent from a year earlier to 950,278 vehicles,
the company said in an e-mailed statement.  
 First-half sales of the company’s Audi brand cars in China
rose 64 percent to 109,887 vehicles, according to the statement.  
